race.description: Bet Nation Same Race Multi 5Th Grade
race.comment: RUMBLE TEMPEST (2) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (22.12) from Box 6 at this track. The form out of his last race has been franked. Deserves serious consideration. SHE'S SAINTLY (4) ran below her best last time finishing seventh (29.73) over 498m at this track in a OPEN. Won at her only start from this draw. Cannot be taken lightly. GAS IT UP (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (29.16) at this track behind Aston Bradley in a Restricted WIN. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to be in this for a long way. UNDERBELLY MISS (3) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.
